{
  "stem": "22652.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'd like, if I may, I'd like to describe a day and a holiday, because that-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The nuns were very nice to us, but there were hundreds and hundreds of children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd like to mention that half of the-- what seemed to be like an orphanage, some of the children were delinquent, or they were abandoned by parents who were criminals.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so it was like, like a juvenile hall, and it was like a jail.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because of it, because of government looking after them, they were well fed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of those children, they had brother and sister in our part.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were in the part of [FRENCH] abandoned children, and, as I said, some of the children had brother and sister in the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had visiting days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very austere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very strict.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rules were very strict.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We usually got up at 4:00 or 5:00 AM, and the region of Grenoble was freezing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember just freezing weather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my hands and feet were covered with blisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I pulled the glove or the socks, part of the flesh went with it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were hungry all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got up at 4:00 or 5:00 AM, and we went to Mass in the chapel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always liked the Mass, because I was in the children's choir.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I liked the music.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the chapel was pretty, and it was warm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it-- and, and enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I enjoyed the whole Mass liturgy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in Latin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember talking to a nun, and she said, you must have faith.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I've always thought about that word, avoir la foi.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
